---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for AvinashBlog — AdSense and cookie disclosure."
  noIndex={false}
>
  <div class="container privacy-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>AvinashBlog ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy describes what information we collect and how we use it.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Google AdSense & Advertising</h2>
      <p>This site uses Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based on your visits to this and other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>
      <p>Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to this website or other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visit to this site and/or other sites on the internet.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Display relevant advertisements (Google AdSense)</li>
        <li>Analyze site traffic (if analytics is enabled)</li>
        <li>Remember your preferences</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect the functionality of this site.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — advertising. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN and hosting. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>This is a static website. We do not directly collect personal information such as names or email addresses unless you contact us. Server logs may automatically collect IP addresses and browser information for security purposes.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page indicates when it was last revised.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .updated { color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  section { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  h2 { font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  ul { padding-left: var(--space-6); list-style: disc; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-2); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  li { color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  a { color: var(--color-primary); }
</style>
